    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken thighs,</strong> <strong>beetroot quarters</strong> and <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a baking tray</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Drizzle everything with <strong>olive oil</strong>, season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min</p>",
