    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely grate your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>orange[s]</strong> in half</p>",
