    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> [260ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated ginger</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>tamarind paste</strong>, <strong>honey</strong> and a squeeze of <strong>orange juice</strong></p><p>Give everything a good stir – this is your <strong>sticky orange & tamarind sauce</strong></p>",
